1. *Zato* se trudim da budem lepši. (That's why I'm trying to be nicer.)
2. Ja *zato* ne mogu da verujem. (That's why I can't believe it.)
3. *Zato* treba da se pripremiš. (That's why you should prepare.)
4. On je *zato* prekinuo vezu. (That's why he broke up.)
5. *Zato* sam rešio da odem. (That's why I decided to go.)
6. *Zato* je ona bila ljuta. (That's why she was angry.)
7. *Zato* smo se odselili. (That's why we moved away.)
8. *Zato* su oni otišli. (That's why they left.)